### Update Onboarding Data

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/settings/onboarding/update/9/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "hormonalInfo": {
        "regularCycle": true,
        "currentPhase": "Follicular",
        "cycleLength": 30,
        "periodLength": 4,
        "birthControlHRT": false,
        "hasUterus": false
    },
    "dailyReminders": {
        "dailyReminder": true,
        "reminderTime": "10:00"
    },
    "aiInsights": {
        "showFENYXInsights": false
    },
    "lifestylePreferences": {
        "dietaryStyles": [1, 2, 3],
        "activityLevel": 2,
        "stressLevel": 2,
        "medications": "Multivitamin"
    }
}

### Retrieve Onboarding Data
GET {{baseUrl}}/settings/onboarding/details/9/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### List Onboarding Data
GET {{baseUrl}}/settings/onboarding/details/ 
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}